You need to wait until the image has loaded before calling ctx.drawImage(). <dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>img.onload = function() { ctx.drawImage(img); };</code></dd></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4">zcorpan</a> — Sat Jun 16, 2012 12:03 pm</p><hr />
